Actual Version : v6.3.2 / Date :02-Aug-2002
----------------

Notes          : 
----------------

New Features   :
----------------
- RAP for detail reject:
  needs an activated the FCT_IRules with the TAP3_VAL ruleset loaded in the database
- RAP for Batch reject
  the checks for Batch validity is not implemented in the input grammar. Only the 
  processing (error messaging, rollback request, rap generation) is implemented.
  the checks have to be implemented, and when a check fails, the already built 
  requestBatchReject() function must be called which take care of the rest.

Known Problems :
----------------

Solved PRs/CRs :
----------------
- PRSF00015604 : AccountingInfo.Taxation.TaxRateDefinition.TaxType always set to "15".
  The TaxType is now set to "13" which is ValueAddedTax.
- PRSF00015605 : TAP3 MOC mapping ignores mandatory element CalledCountryCode for 
  international call type.
  Now we have a new EDR field: DETAIL.CALLED_COUNTRY_CODE which must contain the
  destination CountryCode in case of an international call

